attributes.text: At the roundabout, take the first exit onto Grassie Blvd
Take the exit on the right to MB-101 W / Perimeter Hwy
Keep left at the fork to merge onto Perimeter Hwy (MB-101)
Take exit 69 on the right toward City Rte-180 / MB-8 / Gimli / McPhillips St
Keep left at the fork to McPhillips St (MB-8)
Keep right at the fork to merge onto Mc Phillips St toward City Rte-180 S
Finish at Location 2, on the left
